  33:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  * STEVAL_MKI109V3    - Host side:   USB (Virtual COM)
  34:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *                    - Sensor side: SPI(Default) / I2C(supported)
  35:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *
  36:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  * NUCLEO_STM32F401RE - Host side: UART(COM) to USB bridge
  37:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *                    - I2C(Default) / SPI(N/A)
  38:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *
  39:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  * DISCOVERY_SPC584B  - Host side: UART(COM) to USB bridge
  40:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *                    - Sensor side: I2C(Default) / SPI(supported)
  41:Core/Src/hts221_read_data_polling.c ****  *
